'''''Star Wars'' 38''' is the thirty-eighth issue of the [[Star Wars Legends|Legends]] [[Star Wars comic books|comic book]] series [[Star Wars: Republic|''Star Wars'']]. It was written by [[John Ostrander]], illustrated by [[Davidé Fabbri]] and [[Christian Dalla Vecchia]], and first published by [[Dark Horse Comics]] on [[January 23]], [[2002]]. It features the story "'''The Stark Hyperspace War Part Three of Four'''," in which the story of the [[Stark Hyperspace War/Legends|titular war]] continues, and [[Padawan/Legends|Padawans]] [[Obi-Wan Kenobi/Legends|Obi-Wan Kenobi]] and [[Quinlan Vos/Legends|Quinlan Vos]] endure dangers on [[Troiken/Legends|Troiken]].

==Publisher's summary==
''Star Wars: The Stark Hyperspace War'' gets more intense. To prevent the Republic Senate from surrendering, the Jedi must get Senator Valorum back to Coruscant. The assaults grow heavier on the remnants of the Republic forces on Troiken and the fragile defense falls increasingly to Plo Koon. Can Qui-Gon Jinn find the secret of the virus that has corrupted the Republic nav computers and open up the hyperspace lanes to the Republic again? Meanwhile, Tholme and his apprentice, Quinlan Vos, struggle to get what they've learned back to the other Jedi.''''

==Plot summary==
{{Plot|comic}}

==Continuity==
{{Quote|Quinlan and I were on Tatooine the last time Qui-Gon was there. We heard about his death just before we left. Quinlan regretted not contacting him. We were working undercover and he wasn't aware that Qui-Gon's need was so desperate.|Aayla Secura|<ref name="Star Wars (1998) 38">[[Star Wars (1998) 38|''Star Wars'' (1998) 38]]</ref>}}
The issue's front matter states: "The events in this [[Star Wars: Republic|series]] take place 30 [[Standard year/Legends|years]] prior to [[Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope|''Star Wars: A New Hope'']]," which corresponds to [[30 BBY/Legends|30 BBY]].

In this issue, the [[Aayla Secura/Legends|Aayla Secura]] acknowledges the [[Retroactive continuity|retroactive]] cameo made by Quinlan Vos in the [[1999]] film [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''The Phantom Menace'']].<ref name="Phantom Menace">{{Film|I}}</ref>

